item.description:
$where[] = [&#39;level&#39;, &#39;=&#39;, 1]; $where[] = [&#39;level&#39;, &#39;=&#39;, 2]; $user = UserModel::whereOr($where)-&gt;select(); where与whereOr混写（条件1 and (条件2 or 条件3)）  遇到whereOr和where组合链式操作使用闭包条件统一写到闭包里面 会自动加上括号. 改写链式查询条件为以下:
 $where[] = [&#39;level&#39;, &#39;=&#39;, 1]; $where[] = [&#39;level&#39;, &#39;=&#39;, 2]; $user = UserModel::where(&#39;条件1&#39;)-&gt;where(function ($query) use ($where) { $query-&gt;where(&#39;条件2&#39;)-&gt;whereOr($where) })-&gt;select(); 查询时间范围 $rangeData[&#39;sell_date&#39;] = [&#39;egt&#39;=&gt;$date_start_day,&#39;elt&#39;=&gt;$date_end_day];  一个字段多个值查询
 $where[] = [&#39;level&#39;, &#39;=&#39;, 1]; $where[] = [&#39;level&#39;, &#39;=&#39;, 2]; 或 $whereOr[] = [&#39;shop_name&#39;,&#39;in&#39;,$shops];
